database.name: VIEW M_SOL_RESERVED_STOCK_V
database.view: SELECT rs.m_reservation_stock_id AS m_sol_reserved_stock_v_id, rs.ad_client_id, rs.ad_org_id, rs.isactive, rs.created, rs.createdby, rs.updated, rs.updatedby, rs.m_reservation_stock_id, r.m_reservation_id, r.c_orderline_id FROM m_reservation_stock rs JOIN m_reservation r ON rs.m_reservation_id = r.m_reservation_id
